    "We tested our prompts on our sample case, SEC v. Kaplan, et al.",
    "The Law360 articles used in our prompts were the following: Perera (2023), Guarnaccia (2019), Ruscoe (2019), Sinay (2020a, b), Archer (2016), Newsham (2018), Kochman (2018), Wichert (2018), Jarvis (2022) and Innis (2022).",
    "For further details of our prompt design process, see \"Appendix 3.2\".",
    "We note that, for this part of our research, we were unable to use the OpenAI API.",
    "When we submitted our prompts to the API, we received an error."
